: 936, \"to\": 939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medals have yet to be awarded and Chock and her teammates want to receive the medals in an Olympic atmosphere as soon as possible.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4190159683055996e-37, \"text\": \"Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Medals\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic atmosphere\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have thought about it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We would like to have a true Olympic medal ceremony.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a true Olympic medal ceremony\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For us, that would be a ceremony at the Paris Olympics this summer... surrounded by the Olympic spirit.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"a ceremony\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That would be the dream scenario.\\\"\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dream scenario\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following CAS' decision, Valieva being dropped from Russia's team scoring lifted the US squad into the gold medal spot in a re-ranking announced on Jan 29 by the International Skating Union (ISU).\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3251877413469633e-32, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966764445882951, \"rank\": 0.0033125050607109158, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9586309771001664, \"rank\": 0.04271627618279741, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999989286152, \"rank\": 9.773946088471252e-10, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Skating_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.593792106601641e-32, \"text\": \"ISU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Skating_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Skating_Union\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Valieva\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal spot\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"Jan\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"