States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Appeals\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"chief executive officer\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medals\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been given clear direction we should proceed with giving medals to the US team and that's what we are going to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9586309771001664, \"rank\": 0.04271627618279741, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clear direction\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no scenario in which Team USA is not the gold medal winner and we are eager to get these medals awarded.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.6694687408976994, \"rank\": 0.23368328530247098, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no scenario\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal winner\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"these medals\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everybody has a sense of urgency.\\\"\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everybody\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"urgency\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chock added that when the controversy first unfolded two years ago, she never expected it would take this long to resolve.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chock\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"this long\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a small underlying feeling of disappointment and sadness,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small underlying feeling\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2204}, {\"ngram\": \"sadness\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not realise it had been weighing on us the whole time until we got the resolution.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the resolution\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's like a weight has been lifted.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a weight\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like we are celebrating our Olympic experience all over again.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It puts a feeling of closure to this whole movement and the Beijing Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a feeling\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"closure\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"this whole movement\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beijing Olympics\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And at age 31, Chock can finally call herself an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4190159683055996e-37, \"text\": \"Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Amazing, quite frankly,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A feeling I have always dreamt of, one I almost can not believe is finally here.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A feeling\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a very happy 24 hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very happy 24 hours\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bates added that the past day had been \\\"surreal\\\" and unbelievable\\\" after the long delay.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2728, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.576265741259716e-17, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past day\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the long delay\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a long and arduous wait,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long and arduous wait\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\